== Summary ==
A VRChat graphic, demonstrating the [[Fallbacks|Fallback]] Avatar System.

Alt-text: "Fallback Avatar System". No Quest version of your Avatar? -You can pick an Avatar to replace the [[Robot]] on Quest. -Your Fallback is scaled to match your size. Menu -> Avatars -> Change Quest to choose your Fallback. People on Quest will see that avatar instead of a gray robot.

Source: https://medium.com/vrchat/vrchat-on-quest-avatar-performance-woes-1a3cc228a442
Secondary source: https://docs.vrchat.com/docs/vrchat-202115

